with%20Sara%20Goodacre%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20evolutionary%20biology%20who%20studies%20how%20spider%20silk%20can%20be%20used%20in%20medicine%20and%20engineering.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20always%20question%20a%20spider%20scare%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20I%20read%20about%20a%20man%20who%20went%20on%20holiday%20and%20said%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcruise-passenger-said-spider-laid-eggs-in-toe-experts-unlikely-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espider%20had%20laid%20eggs%20in%20his%20toe%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20clearly%20had%20a%20serious%20problem%20with%20his%20toe%2C%20but%20spiders%20have%20never%20been%20known%20to%20lay%20eggs%20inside%20a%20human%20body%2C%20and%20the%20wound%20responded%20to%20antibiotics%2C%20which%20do%20nothing%20against%20spider%20venom.%20Biologically%2C%20it%20didn't%20make%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20annoys%20me%20is%20how%20many%20people%20are%20misled%20by%20such%20spider%20stories%20in%20the%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20shouldn't%20be%20devoting%20any%20of%20our%20energy%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsafe-accessible-modes-video-games-tackle-fears-spiders-deep-water-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efearing%20spiders%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20very%20rare%20spiders%20can%20cause%20harm%20to%20humans%2C%20but%2C%20as%20I%20tell%20my%20children%2C%20spiders%20are%20far%20less%20likely%20to%20hurt%20you%20than%20cars%20or%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20are%20scared%20of%20spiders%2C%20here's%20what%20you%20should%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EVenom%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20misconception%20is%20that%20all%20spider%20venom%20causes%20harm%20to%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20spiders%20are%20indeed%20venomous%20to%20humans%2C%20and%20you%20should%20make%20yourself%20aware%20of%20any%20spiders%20that%20could%20hurt%20you%20in%20your%20area%20%E2%80%94%20for%20instance%2C%20in%20the%20US%20you%20want%20to%20know%20how%20to%20spot%20a%20brown%20recluse%20and%20what%20to%20do%20in%20the%20rare%20case%20of%20an%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20spiders%20evolved%20to%20use%20their%20venom%20on%20insects.%20It%20simply%20doesn't%20work%20on%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHouse%20spiders%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20when%20a%20big%20spider%20comes%20into%20your%20house%2C%20it's%20not%20out%20to%20get%20you%2C%20it's%20a%20teenage%20male%20spider%20looking%20for%20a%20female.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20better%20off%20feeling%20a%20bit%20sorry%20for%20him.%20This%20gangly%20youngster%20can't%20sprint%20very%20far%20and%20is%20terrified%20of%20your%20shadow%2C%20which%20it%20probably%20thinks%20is%20a%20bird%20coming%20to%20eat%20it.%20If%20it%20darts%20your%20way%2C%20it%20is%20not%20following%20you%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20just%20trying%20to%20stay%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20see%20a%20spider%20in%20your%20bathroom%2C%20you're%20better%20off%20just%20leaving%20it%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20want%20to%20use%20energy%20to%20escape%20from%20you%2C%20so%20unless%20you%20scare%20it%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20to%20fall%20on%20your%20head.%20It%20will%20just%20sit%20there%20until%20night%20when%20it%20will%20go%20eat%20the%20mosquitoes%20on%20your%20window%20sill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20suggest%20that%20people%20name%20the%20spider%20under%20their%20sofa.%20We%20always%20used%20to%20call%20ours%20Christopher.%20It's%20really%20hard%20to%20squash%20a%20Christopher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESwallowing%20spiders%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20that%20you%20swallow%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20spiders%20every%20night%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fwellness%2F2023%2F10%2F31%2Fswallow-8-spiders-sleep%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20urban%20myth%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20spiders%20walk%20around%20at%20night%2C%20but%20why%20would%20they%20deliberately%20venture%20into%20a%20weird%2C%20warm%2C%20humid%20mouth%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20probably%20do%20get%20eaten%20by%20humans%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20just%20as%20people%20will%20sometimes%20swallow%20a%20passing%20fly%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20exception%20rather%20than%20the%20norm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20spiders%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faustralian.museum%2Flearn%2Fanimals%2Fspiders%2Fspider-facts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edon't%20seem%20to%20harm%20that%20many%20people%20globally%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20there%20are%20antivenoms%20for%20dangerous%20spiders%20such%20as%20the%20funnel-web%20spider%20or%20the%20black%20widow%20spider%2C%20which%20greatly%20reduces%20the%20risk%20of%20dying%20after%20a%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%20you%20see%20a%20spider%2C%20ask%20yourself%20if%20the%20injury%20could%20have%20been%20caused%20by%20a%20cut%20infected%20by%20microbes%20instead%20and%20check%20your%20facts%20with%20a%20local%20reputable%20society%20of%20arachnologists.%20We're%20not%20afraid%20to%20say%20it%20exactly%20as%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-not-be-scared-spiders-arachnophobia-expert-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703934001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658ee6a81c5c7b8c9a0cd335%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-not-be-scared-spiders-arachnophobia-expert-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sara%20Goodacre%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20evolutionary%20biology%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20why%20people%20shouldn't%20be%20scared%20of%20spiders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mguenot%40businessinsider.com%20(Marianne%20Guenot)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-not-be-scar