tors-in-2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%2014%20million%20tourists%20who%20visit%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20city%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20blazers%20were%20OK%20for%20working%20in%20air%20conditioning%2C%20but%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20packed%20a%20few%20more%20light%2C%20summery%20dresses%20for%20the%20time%20I%20spent%20sightseeing%20since%20it's%20hot%20in%20Dubai.%20Temperatures%20hit%20nearly%2090%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20or%2032%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20each%20day%20in%20early%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMake%20time%20to%20visit%20Sharjah%20if%20you're%20interested%20in%20Emirati%20heritage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222122%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Al-Hisn%20Fort%20in%20Sharjah%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658c9563ab6f2ebb11f73f83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221412%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20restored%20Al-Hisn%20Fort%20in%20Sharjah's%20heritage%20area.%3Cp%3EWalter%20Bibikow%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20some%20of%20the%20most%20well-known%20Dubai%20attractions%2C%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-largest-water-park-dubai-aquaventure-thrill-seekers-dream-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20park%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Burj%20Khalifa.%20But%20I%20recommend%20spending%20some%20time%20in%20Sharjah%20to%20learn%20about%20Emirati%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20third-most%20populous%20city%20in%20UAE%20and%20one%20of%20seven%20Emirates%20that%20make%20up%20the%20country.%20Depending%20on%20traffic%2C%20Sharjah%20is%20about%2025%20minutes%20to%20an%20hour%20north%20of%20Dubai.%20The%20best%20way%20to%20get%20there%20is%20by%20taxi%2C%20which%20could%20cost%20up%20to%20%2430%2C%20according%20to%20locals%20I%20spoke%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20heritage%20area%20in%20Sharjah%20where%20you%20can%20visit%20museums%20sho