icare%20coverage%20would%20be%20tough%2C%20because%20the%20costs%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20high%20and%20increase%20seniors'%20premiums%2C%20the%20analysts%20said.%20One%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMp2300516%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Vanderbilt%20University%20researchers%20estimated%20that%20if%20just%2010%25%20of%20Medicare%20beneficiaries%20were%20treated%20with%20Wegovy%2C%20the%20cost%20to%20the%20program%20would%20total%20%2426.8%20billion%20a%20year%2C%20or%20almost%20a%20fifth%20of%20what%20Medicare%20Part%20D%20spent%20on%20prescription%20drugs%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20competition%20could%20help%20improve%20access%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-drugs-ozempic-cost-more-in-america-than-uk-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eprices%20of%20weight-loss%20drugs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20drop%20as%20competing%20treatments%20come%20to%20market%20and%20drugmakers%20introduce%20oral%20versions%20that%20are%20cheaper%20to%20manufacture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20intense%20competition%20over%20time%20will%20likely%20drive%20prices%20south%2C%20which%20would%20drive%20access%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bill%20Coyle%2C%20global%20head%20of%20biopharma%20at%20consulting%20firm%20ZS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20rivalry%20between%20the%20two%20makers%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fnew-weight-loss-drugs-popularity-evidence-and-side-effects-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eobesity%20shots%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20market%20is%20already%20pushing%20prices%20lower.%20Eli%20Lilly%20set%20the%20list%20price%20of%20its%20new%20weight-loss%20drug%20Zepbound%20about%2020%25%20lower%20than%20Novo%20Nordisk's%20Wegovy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drugmakers%20are%20also%20offering%20coupons%20for%20patients%20to%20try%20the%20drugs%20at%20significant%20discounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20more%20obesity%20drugs%20are%20being%20developed%2C%20though%20it%20could%20be%20several%20years%20before%20they%20hit%20pharmacy%20shelves.%20David%20Risinger%2C%20senior%20managing%20director%20at%20Leerink%2C%20said%20he%20anticipates%20the%20first%20oral%20anti-obesity%20drug%20from%20Eli%20Lilly%2C%20called%20orforglipron%2C%20will%20launch%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELilly%20is%20also%20developing%20an%20injectable%20drug%2C%20called%20retatrutide%2C%20that%20may%20be%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20shots%20on%20the%20market%20today.%20One%20clinical%20trial%20found%20that%20patients%20with%20obesity%20who%20took%20the%20drug%2C%20which%20mimics%20three%20different%20hunger-regulating%20hormones%2C%20lost%2024%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%20on%20average%20in%20just%2011%20months.%20That%20drug%20could%20launch%20in%202027%2C%20Risinger%20said%2C%20but%20he%20warned%20it%20might%20be%20priced%20higher%20than%20competitors%20because%20of%20its%20stronger%20efficacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENovo%20Nordisk%20and%20a%20number%20of%20other%20pharma%20companies%20have%20other%20obesity%20drugs%20in%20various%20stages%20of%20development%2C%20some%20similar%20to%20the%20treatments%20on%20the%20market%20and%20others%20that%20work%20in%20new%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELonger%20term%2C%20the%20patents%20protecting%20the%20drugs%20will%20expire%2C%20clearing%20the%20path%20for%20cheaper%20generic%20versions.%20Novo%20Nordisk's%20patent%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fweight-loss-drugs-ranked-effectiveness-medical-guidelines-wegovy-semaglutide-saxenda-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESaxenda%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20earlier%20obesity%20shot%20approved%20by%20the%20FDA%20in%202014%2C%20is%20set%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F353278%2F000162828023001868%2Fnvo-20221231.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eexpire%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20estimated%20that%20key%20patents%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-weight-loss-meds-injections-compare-costs-results-side-effects%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWegovy%2C%20Ozempic%2C%20and%20Mounjaro%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20won't%20expire%20until%20early%20to%20mid-2030s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPharma%20companies%20say%20these%20drugs%20do%20more%20for%20your%20health%20than%20just%20weight%20loss%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20pharma%20companies%20are%20busy%20pumping%20out%20more%20evidence%20that%20their%20drugs%20improve%20people's%20health%2C%20beyond%20weight%20loss.%20They're%20also%20trying%20to%20persuade%20employers%20and%20insurers%20that%20those%20health%20benefits%20can%20save%20them%20money%20by%20reducing%20how%20much%20they%20spend%20on%20patients'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fobesity-expert-says-why-ok-patient-weighing-300-pounds-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eweight-related%20conditions%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20hoping%20that%20all%20of%20this%20data%20will%20convince%20more%20doctors%20to%20prescribe%20their%20drugs%20and%20more%20health%20plans%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENovo%20Nordisk%20has%20a%20head%20start.%20In%20November%2C%20it%20asked%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-obesity-drug-fda-approved-wegovy-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFDA%20to%20approve%20Wegovy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20drug%20to%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20major%20heart%20problems%2C%20after%20it%20found%20that%20the%20obesity%20drug%20lowered%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20attacks%2C%20strokes%2C%20and%20cardiovascular%20death%20by%2020%25%20in%20people%20with%20existing%20heart%20disease.%20If%20Wegovy's%20label%20expands%2C%20doctors%20could%20prescribe%20it%20as%20a%20heart%20drug%2C%20sidestepping%20insurers'%20weight-loss%20exclusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENovo%20and%20Eli%20Lilly%20are%20also%20studying%20whether%20their%20drugs%20could%20help%20people%20with%20conditions%20such%20as%20sleep%20apnea%2C%20chronic%20kidney%20disease%2C%20and%20musculoskeletal%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExpect%20much%2C%20much%20more%20outcome%20data%20over%20the%20coming%20quarters%20and%20years.%20That's%20going%20to%20be%20key%2C%26quot%3B%20Patrik%20Jonsson%2C%20president%20of%20Lilly%20USA%2C%20said%20at%20the%20UBS%20BioPharma%20Conference%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECould%20weight-loss%20drugs%20change%20how%20the%20US%20pays%20for%20prescriptions%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmericans'%20hunger%20for%20weight-loss%20drugs%2C%20and%20the%20shockwaves%20it's%20likely%20to%20send%20through%20the%20culture%20and%20economy%2C%20are%20only%20just%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effects%20are%20already%20being%20felt%20by%20plenty%20of%20businesses%2C%20even%20beyond%20healthcare%2C%20as%20Wall%20Street%20attempts%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20widespread%20use%20of%20GLP-1s%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-ozempic-wegovy-glp1-weight-loss-drugs-investing-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereshape%20every%20industry%20from%20food%20to%20transportation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Walmart%20has%20said%20shoppers%20are%20buying%20less%20food.%20Airlines%20are%20excited%20about%20the%20potential%20to%20save%20on%20fuel%20with%20lighter%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJefferies%20analysts%20estimated%20that%20the%20US%20market%20for%20obesity%20drugs%20could%20reach%20more%20than%20%24100%20billion%20by%202031%2C%20as%2030%20million%20to%2035%20million%20people%20with%20obesity%20seek%20out%20GLP-1%20therapies.%20That's%20only%20about%2015%25%20of%20people%20with%20obesity%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoyle%2C%20of%20ZS%2C%20said%20obesity%20drugs%2C%20along%20with%20other%20expensive%20treatments%20that%20could%20be%20used%20by%20large%20groups%20of%20people%2C%20such%20as%20future%20breakthrough%20Alzheimer's%20therapies%2C%20might%20be%20the%20catalyst%20that%20changes%20how%20the%20US%20pays%20for%20high-cost%20prescriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20healthcare%20systems%20and%20the%20pharma%2F%20healthcare%20system%20interactions%20work%20today%2C%20they%20don't%20support%20products%20with%20that%20kind%20of%20short-term%20budget%20impact%20and%20long-term%20value.%20Most%20other%20things%20you%20can%20absorb.%20You%20can%20absorb%20a%20%241%20million%20drug%20for%20a%20few%20dozen%20people.%26quot%3B%20He%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BSomething%20that%20treats%20100%20million%20patients%20in%20the%20U.S%20does%20not%20fit%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20healthcare%20system%20very%20effectively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20Carolina%20Treasurer%20Dale%20Folwell%20knows%20this%20firsthand.%20He%20oversees%20the%20state%20employee%20health%20plan%2C%20which%20saw%20costs%20skyrocket%20as%20thousands%20of%20workers%20suddenly%20started%20taking%20weight-loss%20drugs.%20The%20plan%20expects%20to%20spend%20%24112%20million%20on%20those%20drugs%20this%20year%2C%20up%20from%20%2461%20million%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFolwell%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nctreasurer.com%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Ftreasurer-folwell-calls-novo-nordisk-lower-unfair-cost-weight-loss-drugs%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTreasurer%2520Dale%2520R.%2CNordisk%252C%2520prices%2520the%2520drugs%2520fairly.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecalled%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20plan%20to%20stop%20covering%20the%20drugs%20until%20Novo%20Nordisk%20lowers%20its%20prices.%20The%20extreme%20costs%20threaten%20the%20plan's%20solvency%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20there%20would%20be%20no%20other%20option%20than%20to%20triple%20all%20workers'%20premiums%20if%20the%20plan%20keeps%20coverage%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20North%20Carolina%20has%20landed%20on%20a%20compromise%20for%20state%20workers.%20People%20who%20are%20already%20getting%20weight-loss%20drugs%20will%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20taking%20them.%20But%20new%20prescriptions%20won't%20be%20covered%2C%20starting%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20no%20question%20about%20the%20efficacy%20of%20these%20drugs%2C%26quot%3B%20Folwell%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20deep%20concerns%20about%2C%20obviously%2C%20the%20price%20of%20the%20drug.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-drug-insurance-coverage-access-employer-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703933221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f21891c5c7b8c9a0cfb8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-drug-insurance-coverage-access-employer-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weight-loss%20drugs%20aren't%20covered%20by%20many%20employer-provided%20insurance%20plans.%20Access%20will%20likely%20reduce%20further%20in%202024%20unless%20competition%20drops%20prices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22slivingston%40businessinsider.com%20(Shelby%20Livingston)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-drug-insurance-coverage-access-employer-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sohail%20and%20Salman%20joke%20about%20their%20love%20lives%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703932896000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106402564%2Cimgsize-42694.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsohail-khan-has-a-hilarious-reaction-on-his-wedding-as-salm