-at-welfare-scheme-beneficiary-home-4768883%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-ayodhya-visit-pm-narendra-modi-takes-detour-for-tea-at-welfare-scheme-beneficiary-home-4768883%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-ayodhya-visit-pm-narendra-modi-takes-detour-for-tea-at-welfare-scheme-beneficiary-home-4768883%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20Years%20After%20Announcement%2C%20Soren%20Govt%20Yet%20to%20Withdraw%20Cases%20Pending%20Against%20Pathalgadi%20Movement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F22171455%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-22-at-3.48.58-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFive%20cases%20registered%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Pathalgadi%20movement%20in%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Kunti%20district%20are%20still%20pending%20to%20be%20withdrawn.%20Four%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20December%202019%2C%20when%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20current%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20took%20over%2C%20he%20vowed%20to%20withdraw%20all%20cases%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20movement%2C%20filed%20under%20his%20predecessor%20Raghubar%20Das%E2%80%99s%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%2021%20cases%20registered%20by%20Das%E2%80%99s%20government%20in%20Khunti%2C%2016%20so%20far%20have%20been%20withdrawn%20under%20the%20Soren%20government.%20In%20March%202020%2C%20the%20Soren%20government%20going%20against%20its%20promise%20filed%20a%20new%20case%20against%20the%20movement.%20The%20pending%20cases%20name%20Stan%20Swamy%20along%20with%2020%20other%20activists%20and%20intellectuals%20associated%20with%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20information%20regarding%20pending%20cases%20has%20been%20disclosed%20by%20replies%20received%20to%20appeals%20filed%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%2C%20said%20Jharkhand%20Janadhikar