0Adivasis%20(PESA%2C%20Fifth%20Schedule%2C%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%20CNT%20Act%2C%20etc.)%2C%20marginalisation%20of%20Adivasi%20worldview%2C%20exploitation%20of%20Adivasis%20by%20the%20police%2C%20administration%2C%20and%20non-Adivasis%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20Janadhikar%20Mahasabha%20has%20been%20demanding%20the%20Soren%20government%20to%20immediately%20withdraw%20all%20five%20pending%20%3Cspan%3EPathalgadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%20cases%2C%20initiate%20action%20against%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20Khunti%2C%20and%20award%20compensation%20to%20victims.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20calling%20for%20the%20strict%20implementation%20of%20special%20laws%20and%20provisions%20for%20Adivasis%20such%20as%20PESA%2C%20Fifth%20Schedule%2C%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%20CNT%20Act%2C%20and%20so%20on%20in%20letter%20and%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703930056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F22171455%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-22-at-3.48.58-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F4-years-after-announcement-soren-govt-yet-to-withdraw-cases-pending-against-pathalgadi-movement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20pending%20cases%20name%20Stan%20Swamy%20along%20with%2020%20other%20activists%20and%20intellectuals%20associated%20with%20the%20movement.%C2%A0On%2029%20December%202019%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20soon%20after%20taking%20the%20oath%20as%20chief%20minister%20had%20announced%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20all%20Pathalgadi%20cases.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F4-years-after-announcement-soren-govt-yet-to-withdraw-cases-pending-against-pathalgadi-movement%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20went%20on%20board%20Beond%2C%20'the%20world's%20first%20premium%20leisure%20airline'%20with%20lie-flat%20beds%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20