ng%20dejectedly.%20It%20was%20like%20our%20hard%20work%20of%20two%20months%20got%20negated%20due%20to%20just%20one%20match.%20It%20was%20our%20bad%20day%20and%20we%20were%20dejected%20but%20when%20the%20PM%20enters%2C%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20your%20head%20high.%20We%20were%20not%20even%20told%20that%20Modiji%20was%20coming%20there%20and%20suddenly%20he%20entered.%20Earlier%2C%20we%20were%20not%20even%20in%20the%20mood%20to%20eat%20and%20talk%20to%20each%20other%20but%20when%20he%20came%2C%20it%20was%20such%20a%20big%20surprise%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shami.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703929980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fppphhd48_shami-_625x300_02_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammed-shami-took-injections-during-world-cup-report-reveals-india-star-pacers-chronic-issue-4769424%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023's%20highest%20wicket-taker%2C%20could%20have%20been%20handy%20for%20India%20vs%20South%20Africa%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammed-shami-took-injections-during-world-cup-report-reveals-india-star-pacers-chronic-issue-4769424%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammed-shami-took-injections-during-world-cup-report-reveals-india-star-pacers-chronic-issue-4769424%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammed-shami-took-injections-during-world-cup-report-reveals-india-star-pacers-chronic-issue-4769424%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Airstrikes%20over%20eastern%20Syria%20near%20Iraqi%20border%20kills%20six%20Iran-backed%20militants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703929627000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106401577%2Cimgsize-34788.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%