t-their-us-home-police-suspect-domestic-violence-4768218%5C%22%3Epreliminary%20investigation%20points%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeadly%20incident%20of%20domestic%20violence%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20no%20outside%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kamal%20family%2C%20originally%20from%20India%2C%20had%20established%20themselves%20within%20the%20tech%20industry%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20used%20to%20run%20an%20education%20systems%20company%20called%20EduNova.%20The%20company%20is%20now%20defunct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20Becoming%20Millionaires%20To%20Bankruptcy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakesh%20Kamal%2C%20an%20alumnus%20of%20Boston%20University%2C%20the%20MIT%20Sloan%20School%20of%20Management%2C%20and%20Stanford%20University%2C%20had%20an%20extensive%20career%20in%20education%20consulting%20and%20launched%20an%20Ed-tech%20company%20with%20his%20wife%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEduNova%20marketed%20a%20'student%20success%20system'%20designed%20to%20improve%20the%20grades%20of%20students%20in%20middle%20school%2C%20high%20school%2C%20and%20college%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Boston%20Globe%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20initially%20performed%20well%20resulting%20in%20the%20Kamals%20purchasing%20the%2019%2C000-square-foot%20estate%20%E2%80%93%20which%20boasts%2011%20bedrooms%20%E2%80%93%20for%20%244%20million%20in%202019%2C%20according%20to%20state%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fjfehpmus_indian-couple-murdered_625x300_30_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20company%20was%20dissolved%20in%20December%202021%2C%20the%20records%20show.%20This%20was%20the%20start%20of%20a%20financial%20crisis%20for%20the%20couple%2C%20who%20used%20to%20go%20around%20as%20Rick%20and%20Teena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20sprawling%20mansion%20went%20into%20foreclosure%20a%20year%20ago%20and%20was%20sold%20to%20the%20Massachusetts-based%20Wilsondale%20Associates%20LLC%20for%20%243%20million.%20The%20estate%20was%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20%245.45%20million%20when%20it%20was%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeena%20Kamal%2C%20an%20alumna%20of%20Harvard%20University%20and%20Delhi%20University%20in%20India%2C%20also%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20in%20September%202022%2C%20further%20highlighting%20the%20financial%20distress%20that%20the%20couple%20was%20under.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happened%20On%20Thursday%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECops%20received%20a%20call%20at%207.24%20pm%20on%20Thursday%20evening%20from%20a%20relative%20of%20the%20Kamal%20family%20who%20had%20come%20to%20check%20on%20them%20after%20not%20hearing%20from%20them%20for%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20members%20of%20the%20Kamal%20family%20were%20the%20only%20ones%20living%20in%20the%20mansion%20at%20the%20time%2C%20officials%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20area%2C%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20in%20the%20state%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20nice%20neighbourhood%2C%20a%20safe%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fs25074sk_indian-couple-murdered_625x300_30_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20of%20Rakesh%2C%20Teena%2C%20and%20Ariana%20were%20found%20inside%20the%20house%20when%20police%20arrived%20at%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Norfolk%20District%20Attorney%20said%20that%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20give%20a%20definitive%20motive%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Bterrible%20tragedy%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20probe%20is%20still%20on%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20happened.%20He%20said%20that%20only%20after%20the%20med