e%5C%22%3EDinesh%20Karthik%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20blamed%20the%20%26quot%3Black%20of%20skill%26quot%3B%20for%20India's%20crushing%20defeat%20to%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20earlier%20this%20week.%20South%20Africa%20beat%20India%20by%20an%20innings%20and%2032%20runs%20at%20the%20SportSport%20Park%20in%20Centurion%2C%20taking%20a%201-0%20lead%20in%20the%20two-match%20series.%20India%20scored%20just%20245%20runs%20in%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20while%20also%20allowing%20South%20Africa%20to%20post%20408.%20After%20conceding%20a%20lead%20of%20163%20runs%2C%20India%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%20131%20in%20their%20second%20innings%2C%20thus%20crashing%20to%20an%20innings%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20analysing%20the%20match%2C%20Karthik%20blamed%20India's%20middle-order%20batting%2C%20as%20well%20as%20medium%20pacers%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shardul%20Thakur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63779-shardul-narendra-thakur-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShardul%20Thakur%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Prasidh%20Krishna%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107509-prasidh-krishna-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPrasidh%20Krishna%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20the%20main%20reasons%20behind%20the%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it's%20about%20not%20being%20ready%20in%20red%20ball%20cricket.%20But%20I'll%20definitely%20put%20it%20down%20to%20lack%20of%20skill.%20There%20are%20certain%20areas%2C%20which%20are%20gaping%20holes%20in%20the%20current%20Indian%20team.%20The%20two%20big%20areas%20for%20me%20are%20the%203rd%20and%204th%20medium%20pacers%20and%20the%20middle%20order%20batting.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20Indian%20team%20that%20we're%20used%20to%20and%20this%20is%20not%20the%20standard%20that%20they've%20set%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Karthik%2C%20who%20is%20one%20of%20the%20retained%20players%20for%20IP%20team%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%2C%20said%20on