%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-plane-gets-stuck-under-bridge-in-bihar-causes-massive-traffic-jam-4768406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-plane-gets-stuck-under-bridge-in-bihar-causes-massive-traffic-jam-4768406%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-plane-gets-stuck-under-bridge-in-bihar-causes-massive-traffic-jam-4768406%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-Origin%20Couple%2C%20Daughter%20Found%20Dead%20In%20Their%20%245%20Million%20US%20Mansion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20wealthy%20Indian-origin%20couple%20and%20their%20teenage%20daughter%20were%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20%245%20million%20mansion%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Massachusetts%20in%20an%20apparent%20domestic%20violence%20incident%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20of%20Rakesh%20Kamal%2C%2057%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20Teena%2C%2054%2C%20and%20their%2018-year-old%20daughter%2C%20Ariana%2C%20were%20found%20in%20their%20Dover%20mansion%20at%20about%207%3A30%20p.m.%20Thursday%2C%20Norfolk%20District%20Attorney%20(DA)%20Michael%20Morrissey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDover%20is%20about%2032%20kilometres%20southwest%20of%20downtown%20Boston%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeena%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20also%20went%20by%20Rick%2C%20had%20previously%20run%20a%20now-defunct%20education%20systems%20company%20called%20EduNova.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20attorney%2C%20who%20described%20the%20%E2%80%9Cterrible%20tragedy%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdomestic%20violence%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20gun%20was%20found%20near%20the%20husband's%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20declined%20to%20say%20whether%20all%20three%20family%20members%20were%20shot%20dead%20%E2%80%94%20and%20by%20whom%2C%20the%20New%20York%20Post%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorrissey%20said%20he%20was%20waiting%20for%20the%20medical%20examiner's%20ruling%2C%20which%20was%20expected%20soon%2C%20before%20deciding%20whether%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20incident%20as%20a%20murder-suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20attorney%20refused%20to%20speculate%20on%20a%20motive%20for%20the%20slayings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20appeared%20to%20have%20faced%20financial%20problems%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20online%20records%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grim%20discovery%20of%20their%20bodies%20was%20made%20after%20a%20relative%20had%20stopped%20by%20to%20check%20on%20the%20family%20members%20after%20not%20hearing%20from%20them%20in%20one%20or%20two%20days%2C%20the%20district%20attorney%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorrissey%20added%20that%20there%20had%20been%20no%20prior%20police%20reports%20or%20domestic%20incidents%20tied%20to%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere's%20been%20no%20police%20reports%2C%20there's%20been%20no%20problems%2C%20no%20domestic%20issues%2C%20no%20nothing%20at%20that%20house%20or%20in%20the%20entire%20neighborhood%20that%20I'm%20aware%20of%2C%E2%80%9D%20Morrissey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20and%20our%20heart%20goes%20out%20to%20the%20entire%20Kamal%20family%20on%20this%20tragedy.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CI%20hate%20to%20see%20it%20at%20any%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Morrissey%20added%20of%20domestic%20violence%20incidents.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20some%20of%20the%20tensions%20that%20people%20feel%20in%20relationships%20often%20come%20out%20around%20the%20holidays.%E2%80%9D%20The%20district%20attorney%20said%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20slayings%20was%20ongoing%20and%20that%20investigators%20had%20worked%20the%20crime%20scene%20through%20much%20of%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20the%20investigation%20is%20at%20a%20very%20preliminary%20stage%2C%20the%20evidence%20available%20at%20this%20time%20does%20not%20indicate%20the%20involvement%20of%20any%20outside%20party%2C%20but%20suggests%20that%20this%20is%20a%20deadly%20incident%20of%20domestic%20violence%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20office%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20believed%20that%20there%20is%20any%20ongoing%20danger%20to%20the%20Dover%20community%20related%20to%20this%20incident.%E2%80%9D%20The%20family's%20sprawling%20mansion%20%E2%80%94%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20%245.45%20million%20%E2%80%94%20went%20into%20foreclosure%20a%20year%20ago%20and%20was%20sold%20to%20the%20Massachusetts-based%20Wilsondale%20Associates%20LLC%20for%20%243%20million%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kamals%20had%20purchased%20the%2019%2C000-square-foot%20estate%20%E2%80%93%20which%20boasts%2011%20bedrooms%20%E2%80%93%20for%20%244%20million%20in%202019%2C%20according%20to%20the%20records%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20members%20were%20the%20only%20ones%20living%20in%20the%20mansion%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20DA%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20area%2C%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20in%20the%20state%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20nice%20neighbourhood%2C%20a%20safe%20community.%E2%80%9D%20Their%20company%20was%20launched%20in%202016%20but%20was%20dissolved%20in%20December%202021%2C%20state%20records%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeena%20Kamal%20was%20listed%20on%20EduNova's%20website%20as%20the%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20the%20company%2C%20describing%20her%20as%20an%20alum%20of%20Harvard%20University%20and%20Delhi%20University%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20biography%20on%20the%20EduNova%20website%2C%20Kamal%20was%20an%20alumnus%20of%20Boston%20University%20and%20the%20MIT%20Sloan%20School%20of%20Management%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Stanford%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20working%20at%20EduNova%2C%20he%20%E2%80%9Cheld%20many%20executive%20positions%20in%20the%20education-consulting%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20biography%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEduNova%20marketed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstudent%20success%20system%E2%80%9D%20designed%20to%20improve%20the%20grades%20of%20students%20in%20middle%20school%2C%20high%20school%2C%20and%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20The%20Boston%20Globe%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeena%20filed%20for%20Chapter%2013%20bankruptcy%20in%20September%202022%20%E2%80%93%20listing%20between%20%241%20million%20and%20%2410%20million%20in%20liabilities%2C%20filings%20show.%20The%20case%2C%20however%2C%20was%20dismissed%20two%20months%20later%20due%20to%20insufficient%20documentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeena%2C%20who%20was%20a%20Harvard%20alumnus%2C%20was%20listed%20as%20one%20of%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20for%20the%20American%20Red%20Cross%20of%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20online%20bio%20touted%20her%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20of%20working%20in%20the%20education%20and%20technology%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20couple's%20daughter%20was%20a%20student%20at%20Middlebury%20College%2C%20a%20%2464%2C800-a-year%20private%20liberal%20arts%20school%20in%20Vermont%2C%20where%20she%20was%20studying%20neuroscience%2C%20according%20to%20her%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorrissey%20also%20said%20a%20homicide%20has%20not%20been%20reported%20in%20Dover%20since%202020%2C%20and%20he%20has%20never%20worked%20a%20homicide%20case%20from%20that%20neighbourhood%20since%20he%20started%20his%20position%20as%20District%20Attorney%2012%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20very%20rare%20to%20have%20this%20kind%20of%20a%20violence%20situation%20almost%20in%20any%20community%20in%20Norfolk%20County%2C%20but%20particularly%20Dover%2C%E2%80%9D%20Morrissey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20a%20small%2C%20well-run%20community%2C%20but%20like%20everybody%20else%2C%20there%20are%20problems%20out%20there%20that%20can%20affect%20no%20matter%20where%20you%20live.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22