So%20far%2C%20the%20election%20commissioners%2C%20including%20the%20CEC%2C%20were%20appointed%20by%20a%20three-member%20panel%20consisting%20of%20the%20PM%2C%20opposition%20nominee%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%20The%20system%20was%20introduced%20following%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20bill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcji-dropped-from-cec-selection-panel-centre-defends-bill-says-supreme-court-ruling-is-followed-11703173327015.html%5C%22%3Epassed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20during%20the%20winter%20session%20excludes%20the%20CJI%20from%20the%20panel.%20The%20CJI%E2%80%99s%20position%20will%20be%20filled%20a%20minister%20nominated%20by%20the%20PM.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%20Modi%20has%20an%20assured%20majority%20in%20the%20three-member%20selection%20panel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20has%20prompted%20the%20retired%20Justice%20Rohington%20F%20Nariman%2C%20a%20former%20solicitor%20general%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fcec-law-be-struck-down-as-arbitrary-severely-imperiling-independence-of-eci-justice-nariman-9070243%5C%22%3Edescribe%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20bill%20as%20one%20severely%20imperilling%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20He%20wanted%20the%20judiciary%20to%20strike%20down%20the%20amended%20act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20CAG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETow%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20last%20bastion%20of%20resistance%20fell.%20Comptroller%20of%20Audit%20and%20Accounts%20was%20totally%20silenced%20in%20October%2C%20when%20Girish%20Murmu%2C%20a%20Gujarat%20cadre%20officer%2C%20was%20appointed%20as%20CAG%20in%20August%202020%2C%20it%20was%20seen%20as%20virtual%20death%20for%20CAG.%20For%2C%20Murmu%20was%20considered%20as%20a%20trusted%20Modi%20aide%20and%20principal%20secretary%20to%20him%20when%20he%20was%20chief%20minister.%20He%20had%20also%20worked%20with%20Amit%20Shah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20deep%20state%20within%20CAG%2C%20an%20institution%20of%20high%20repute%2C%20showed%20signs%20of%20occasional%20resistance.%20Murmu%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20was%20to%20concentrate%20on%20cases%20in%20opposition-ruled%20states%20and%20avoid%20central%20accounts.%20This%20was%20greatly%20successful.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20government%20was%20infuriated%20when%20CAG%20came%20out%20with%20a%20number%20reports%20critical%20of%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Modi%20establishment%20retaliated%20by%20allegedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Findia%2Fcag-auditors-transfer-congress-bharatmala-ayushman-bharat-bjp-18021751.htm%5C%22%3Etransferring%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20officials%20who%20prepared%20the%20offending%20reports.%20Their%20reports%20had%20dented%20the%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20claim%20of%20being%20a%20corruption-free%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20offending%20reports%20had%20brought%20out%20several%20irregularities%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20and%20Dwarka%20Expressway.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decline%20of%20CAG%20under%20Modi%20has%20been%20really%20disheartening.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthewire.in%252Fgovernment%252Fvery-low-number-of-cag-reports-tables-in-parliament-in-2023%2Bcag.%26rlz%3D1C9BKJA_enIN883IN883%26oq%3D%26aqs%3Dchrome.8.69i176j69i59i450l9.438499j1j7%26hl%3Den-US%26sourceid%3Dchrome-mobile%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20showed%20that%20the%20number%20of%20reports%20averaged%2022%20between%202019%20and%202023.%20During%20the%20pre-Modi%20days%20it%20was%20as%20high%20as%2040.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20broad%20position%20as%20