%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndeed%2C%20they%20contend%2C%20what%20we%20dub%20%E2%80%98reality%E2%80%99%20is%20often%20only%20constituted%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20of%20narratives%20which%20owe%20no%20being%20or%20allegiance%20to%20any%20unshakable%20or%20rooted%20truths.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20an%20intellectually%20engaging%20take%20on%20the%20often%20frustrating%20substance%20of%20human%20endeavours%2C%20but%20one%20that%20rather%20cleverly%20evades%20from%20a%20secure%20class%20position%20the%20quite%20determinable%20fact%20that%20such%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%2C%20be%20it%20of%20narratives%20or%20identities%2C%20is%20invariably%20linked%20to%20the%20pursuit%20of%20one%20form%20or%20another%20of%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHuman%20agents%20never%20cease%20to%20deploy%20what%20seem%20inconsistent%20narratives%20to%20obtain%20dominance%20over%20definitions%2C%20institutions%2C%20systems%20of%20governance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20when%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20was%20heard%20to%20make%20reference%20to%20his%20social%20identity%20in%20open%20session%20%E2%80%93%20a%20procedure%20frowned%20upon%20upon%20by%20constitutional%20etiquette%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20drawing%20upon%20a%20social%20resource%20that%20he%20felt%20at%20the%20time%20might%20have%20more%20traction%20among%20a%20television%20audience%20than%20his%20identities%20as%20vice-president%20of%20India%20and%20and%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20mere%20idle%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20of%20an%20identity%20that%20but%20one%20cannily%20directed%20to%20a%20political%20purpose.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20of%20course%20few%20other%20nations%20that%20offer%20quite%20the%20same%20mind-boggling%20spread%20of%20identities%20as%20does%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20fact%20makes%20politics%20in%20India%20both%20endlessly%20frustrating%20and%20fascinating%20all%20at%20once.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELately%2C%20given%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20adroitness%20at%20sophistry%20(making%20false%20arguments%20stand%20for%20the%20lurking%20factual%20ones)%2C%20the%20forthcoming%20general%20elections%20are%20generating%20a%20most%20instructive%20skein%20of%20%E2%80%98takes%E2%80%99%20on%20who%20is%20who%20among%20contenders%20for%20state%20power%20at%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20man%20is%20now%20a%20pure%2C%20socially%20undifferentiated%20nationalist%2C%20and%20now%20a%20protagonist%20of%20this%20or%20that%20social%20group%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20not%20excluded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20latest%20play%20is%20to%20foreground%20some%20demographic%20categories%20as%20the%20real%20four%20castes%20in%20India%2C%20do%20remember%20that%20he%20also%20gently%20reminds%20us%20now%20and%20again%20how%20he%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20numero%20uno%20of%20independent%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20back-and-forth%20of%20owning%20or%20disowning%20identities%20from%20time%20to%20time%20now%20can%20be%20seen%20to%20shape%20the%20canny%20calculations%20of%20segments%20of%20the%20electorate%20across%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20especially.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20that%20context%2C%20a%20pretty%20ingenuous%20and%20politically%20telling%20sample%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20the%207%20o%E2%80%99clock%20evening%20bulletin%20of%20the%20electronic%20news%20channel%2C%20News%2024%2C%20in%20its%20popular%20programme%20%E2%80%98Mahol%20Kya%20Hai%20(what%20is%20the%20political%20weather%20like).%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fmimicry-jagdeep-dhankhar-kalyan-banerjee%5C%22%3EWe%20Were%20Created%20in%20Our%20Creator%E2%80%99s%20Image%20%E2%80%93%20Mimicry%20Is%20Our%20Manifest%20Destiny%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20anchor%20in%20attendance%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20saffron%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esadri%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ereinforced%20by%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekalava%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20around%20his%20wrist%20seemed%20to%20have%20a%20clear-enough%20agenda.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20anxious%20to%20elicit%20from%20his%20exclusive%20Jat%20audience%20in%20Hapur%2C%20a%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20area%2C%20assent%20to%20the%20proposition%20that%20in%20mimicking%20Dhankhar%2C%20the%20political%20opposition%20had%20insulted%20all%20jats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImportant%20to%20note%20that%20this%20programme%20featured%20on%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20the%20late%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20whom%20Jats%20especially%20credit%20with%20having%20been%20not%20just%20their%20tallest%20leader%20%2C%20but%20of%20all%20agriculturists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStunningly%20came%20a%20retort%20that%20the%20only%20authentic%20Jats%20were%20the%20followers%20of%20that%20great%20departed%20leader%20and%2C%20then%2C%20of%20his%20lineage%20now%20led%20by%20his%20grandson%2C%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%3B%20those%20Jats%20who%20had%20their%20loyalties%20elsewhere%20were%20not%20Jats%20but%20Hindus!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20nationalist%20right-wing%20of%20course%20continues%20to%20be%20frustrated%20by%20this%20most%20distressing%20schism%20among%20Indian%20Hindus%3A%20they%20re%20both%20Hindus%20with%20religious%20allegiances%20and%2C%20simultaneously%2C%20proud%20members%20of%20caste%20groups%20which%20they%20uphold%20as%20being%20more%20intimate%20to%20their%20concrete%20and%20grounded%20livelihoods%20than%20their%20rather%20more%20abstruse%20and%20undifferentiated%20religious%20oneness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ruling%20political%20conglomeration%20is%20thus%20constrained%20constantly%20to%20now%20deny%20the%20one%20and%20own%20the%20other%2C%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%20never%20quite%20able%20yet%20to%20extinguish%20the%20social%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20denominational%20as%20its%20monochromatic%20ideological%20purpose%20requires.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20dance%20of%20necessity%20of%20course%20is%20distorted%20by%20grave%20and%20in-your-face%20contradictions%20which%20often%20the%20best%20of%20their%20sophistry%20fails%20to%20eschew.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%2C%20for%20example%2C%20asked%20why%20Dhankhar%E2%80%99s%20proud%20social%20allegiance%20did%20not%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20when%20globally%20decorated%20Jat%20women%20wrestlers%20were%20shamefully%20humiliated%20throughout%20their%20prolonged%20protest%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20alleged%20%E2%80%98sexual%20harassment%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20man%20then%20incharge%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%2C%20only%20very%20pathetic%20and%20lame%20answers%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20from%20the%20spokespersons%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F15093117%2Fdownload-e1684123572882.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F15093117%2Fdownload-e1684123572882.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F15093117%2Fdownload-e1684123572882-300x185.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-653024%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVinesh%20Phogat%2C%20Sangeeta%20Phogal%20and%20Sakshi%20Malik.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40Phogat_Vinesh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEqually%2C%20how%20is%20it%20that%20Dhankhar%20was%20missing%20in%20action%20when%20an%20overwhelmingly%20Jat-constituted%20year-long%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20protest%20in%20the%20worst%20of%20heat%20and%20chill%20held%20its%20ground%20against%20the%20since-withdrawn%20farm%20laws%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fskm-sends-list-of-702-farmers-who-died-during-protest-1057558.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Samyukta%2520Kisan%2520Morcha%2520(SKM%2Cfarm%2520laws%252C%2520to%2520the%2520government.%5C%22%3Ealleged%20deaths%20of%20some%20700%20Jat%2FSikh%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20that%20historic%20protest%20in%20sun%20and%20rain%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20capital%2C%20nor%20the%20ugly%20fact%20that%20they%20were%20dubbed%20%E2%80%98terrorists%E2%80%99%20by%20scions%20of%20the%20establishment%20of%20which%20Dhankhar%20remained%20one%2C%20likewise%20did%20not%20draw%20any%20syllables%20of%20social%20kinship%20from%20the%20honourable%20Dhankhar%20are%20facts%20that%20expose%20the%20un-heroic%20plaint%20that%20Dhankhar%20has%20made%2C%20following%20some%20playful%20inventiveness%20at%20his%20expense%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20might%20have%20amused%20Nehru%20no%20end%20had%20he%20been%20the%20lampooned%20subject.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-jat-farmer-vice-president-kalyan-banerjee%5C%22%3EThe%20Vice-President%20Was%20a%20Jat%20During%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20and%20Wrestlers%E2%80%99%20Protests%20Too%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20new%20and%20charming%20in%20the%20instance%20cited%20above%20is%20how%2C%20in%20a%20new%20twist%20of%20the%20definitional%20play%20of%20identities%2C%20a%20common%20Jat%20thought%20nothing%20of%20distinguishing%20between%20real%20and%20fake%20Jats%2C%20dubbing%20the%20latter%20as%20mere%20%E2%80%98Hindus.%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShould%20such%20perceptions%20fructify%20in%20the%20months%20to%20come%20in%20the%20Hindu-Hindi%20heartland%2C%20the%20republic%20may%20indeed%20be%20set%20to%20witness%20a%20most%20consequential%20replay%20of%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20late%20seventies%20and%20eighties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThink%20how%2C%20even%20as%20it%20decries%20the%20politics%20of%20caste%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20is%20busier%20than%20most%20in%20adding%20on%20as%20many%20caste%20and%20sub-caste%20groups%20to%20its%20alliance%20as%20it%20can%20muster%2C%20while%20also%20hoping%20that%20the%20big%20coming%20event%20of%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20will%20eventually%20subsume%20all%20caste%2Fsocial%20identities%20into%20a%20common%20Hindu-religious%20identity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20nationalist%20right-wing%2C%20thus%2C%20finds%20itself%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20it%20must%20both%20press%20into%20political%20service%20social%2Fcaste%20identities%20as%20do%20the%20opposition%2C%20but%20also%20oppose%20the%20holding%20of%20a%20caste-census%2C%20lest%20a%20social-denominational%20reality%20come%20to%20overwhelm%20its%20project%20of%20religious%20consolidation%20to%20the%20exclusion%20of%20all%20concrete%20social%20realities%20and%20imperatives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it%20is%20comforting%20that%20the%20opposition%20seems%20to%20have%20largely%20succeeded%20in%20quelling%20the%20canny%20narrative%20of%20insult%20to%20Jat%20identity%20via%20the%20mimicking%20of%20Dhankhar%20by%20forcefully%20foregrounding%20the%20more%20real%20and%20consequential%20issues%20of%20ingress%20of%20undesirables%20into%20parliament%2C%20the%20undemocratic%2Funconstitutional%20refusal%20of%20the%20executive%20to%20take%20parliament%20into%20confidence%20on%20it%2C%20and%20the%20unprecedented%20ejection%20of%20practically%20all%20opposition%20lawmakers%20%E2%80%93%20designed%20to%20serve%20two%20governmental%20purposes%3A%20one%2C%20to%20deflect%20from%20accountability%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20to%20avert%20any%20mention%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20intruder%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20the%20House%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fkarnataka%2Fpratap-simhas-path-to-power-paved-with-provocation%5C%22%3Efacilitated%20by%20a%20BJP%20member%20of%20the%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20to%20facilitate%20the%20passage%20of%20more%20than%20one%20potentially%20citizen-retrograde%20legislation%20with%20no%20opposition%20to%20counter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20top%20it%20al%2C%20consider%20that%20while%20the%20entire%20opposition%20has%20been%20thrown%20out%2C%20the%20one%20parliamentarian%20whose%20say-so%20enabled%20the%20intruders%20to%20enter%20parliament%20remains%20both%20unquestioned%20and%20sweetly%20ensconced%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParliamentary%20democracy%2C%20as%20member%20after%20member%20has%20been%20saying%2C%20seems%20truly%20in%20the%20gravest%20jeopardy%2C%20yielding%20everyday%20to%2C%20in%20the%20words%20of%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98police%20state.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20then%2C%20the%20ruling%20right-wing%20seems%20to%20know%20that%20most%20Indians%20prefer%20to%20celebrate%20power%20more%20than%20liberty%2C%20to%20borrow%20the%20felicitous%20phrase%20of%20a%20fellow%20commentator%3B%20and%20many%20seem%20inebriated%20on%20the%20narrative%20that%20%E2%80%98the%20whole%20world%20is%20now%20singing%20praises%20of%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20testifying%20to%20its%20destined%20greatness%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evishwaguru%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20were%20you%20to%20think%20that%20facts%20on%20the%20ground%20do%20not%20warrant%20the%20manufactured%20hype%20and%20euphoria%2C%20why%2C%20who%20more%20anti-national%20than%20you%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENever%20was%20Independence%20as%20fatally%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20a%20destiny%2C%20this%20way%20or%20that%2C%20as%20it%20seems%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20what%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20conclusive%20general%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703828587000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F29111106%2FUntitled-design-15-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-bjp-jat-social-identities%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Never%20was%20Independence%20as%20fatally%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20a%20destiny%2C%20this%20way%20or%20that%2C%20as%20it%20seems%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20what%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20conclusive%20general%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-bjp-jat-social-identities%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Award-winning%20teen%20surfer%20killed%20in%20shark%20attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703820660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F70x70%2Fskynews-khai-cowley-australia_6406508.jpg%3F20231229035712%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fkhai-cowley-australian-teenage-surfer-killed-by-shark-was-standout-talent-13038938%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2015-year-old%20surfer%20killed%20by%20a%20shark%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20South%20Australia%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bstandout%26quot%3B%20talent%2C%20his%20club%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A326%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fkhai-cowley-australian-teenage-surfer-killed-by-shark-was-standout-talent-13038938%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fkhai-cowley-australian-teenage-surfer-killed-by-shark-was-standout-talent-13038938%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fkhai-cowley-australian-teenage-surfer-killed-by-shark-was-standout-talent-13038938%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20Recommends%3A%20The%20Meals%20We%20Remember%20From%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F28182156%2Ffood.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3A%20Shutki%20maccher%20bhorta%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20almost%20two%20years%20since%20my%20grandma%20passed.%20She%20used%20to%20make%20the%20best%20%3Cem%3Eshutki%20maccher%20bhorta%3C%2Fem%3E%20I%E2%80%99ve%20ever%20had.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20Bengali%20preparation%20of%20dried%20loitta%20fish%20slow%20cooked%20with%20sweet%20pumpkin%20and%20a%20lots%20of%20onion%2C%20garlic%20and%20mustard%20oil%20%E2%80%93%20generally%20served%20with%20warm%20white%20rice%20and%20green%20chillies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20used%20to%20have%20it%20with%20Tulaipanji%20rice%2C%20an%20indigenous%20rice%20variety%20of%20North%20Bengal.%20This%20year%20I%20tried%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20to%20recreate%20that%20recipe.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20reach%20my%20grandma%E2%80%99s%20perfection%20but%20it%20was%20worth%20exploring.%20%E2%80%98Shutki%20bhorta%E2%80%99%20is%20very%20inherent%20and%20attached%20to%20our%20%E2%80%98Bangal%E2%80%99%20identity.%20And%20cooking%20it%20here%20in%20Delhi%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20navigate%20the%20urban%20haze%20%E2%80%93%20fulfilling%20yet%20very%20empty%2C%20populated%20yet%20very%20lonely%20and%20green%20yet%20%E2%80%98fresh%E2%80%99%20inside%20the%20plastic%20airtight%20container.%20The%20dish%20bears%20a%20testimony%20to%20my%20childhood%2C%20both%20personally%20and%20politically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Atul%20Ashok%20Howale%3A%20Moving%20to%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20move%20to%20Delhi%20for%20work%20from%20Sangli%2C%20Kolhapur%20%E2%80%93%20a%20city%20famous%20for%20its%20food%20in%20western%20Maharashtra.%20When%20I%20first%20moved%20to%20Delhi%2C%20the%20food%20culture%20was%20a%20drastic%20change.%20The%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20we%20get%20in%20Sangli%20was%20replaced%20by%20momos%20here%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20walking%20in%20Kolhapur%2C%20I%20used%20to%20come%20across%20Kolhapuri%20misal%20within%20evert%20100%20metres%3B%20now%20those%20stalls%20were%20selling%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20bhature%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Erajma%20chawal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20a%20staunch%20non-veg%20food%20lover%20since%20childhood.%20Kolhapur%20Sangli%20is%20very%20famous%20for%20non-veg%20and%20the%20red-white%20gravy%20here%20is%20very%20famous.%20I%20have%20eaten%20non-veg%20at%20many%20places%20in%20Delhi%20%E2%80%93%20and%20when%20I%20first%20started%20out%2C%20all%20if%20it%20felt%20a%20little%20lacking%20in%20spice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20exception%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20went%20to%20Old%20Delhi%2C%20Jama%20Masjid%20in%20the%20month%20of%20Ramzan.%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20the%20small%20food%20street%20in%20Kolhapur.%20Now%20finally%20I%20could%20see%20what%20my%20friend%20in%20Delhi%20had%20been%20saying%20about%20the%20food.%20Making%20my%20way%20through%20the%20crowd%2C%20me%20and%20my%20Maharashtrian%20friend%20Saurabh%20went%20to%20Rahimtullaha%20restaurant.%20We%20ordered%20biryani%20along%20with%20mutton%20korma%2C%20nihari%2C%20and%20their%20famous%20mutton%20and%20chicken%20kebabs.%20This%20was%20my%20first%20kebab%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20was%20amazing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20red%20and%20white%20gravy%20like%20Sangli%20Kolhapur%20in%20Delhi%2C%20today%20that%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20the%20kebabs%20and%20biryani%20of%20Old%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%3A%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20apricot%20jam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20summer%20I%20travelled%20to%20Ladakh%20on%20a%20family%20road%20trip%20after%20over%20a%20decade.%20While%20the%20trip%20came%20with%20its%20many%20ups%20and%20downs%20as%20family%20vacations%20and%20road%20trips%20often%20do%2C%20the%20local%20Apricot%20jam%20sweetened%20the%20experience%20for%20the%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EServed%20as%20a%20breakfast%20staple%20everywhere%20we%20went%2C%20made%20from%20the%20apricot%20trees%20in%20dry%20and%20arid%20Ladakh%2C%20this%20delicious%20jam%20made%20us%20want%20to%20bottle%20up%20all%20that%C2%A0goodness%20and%20bring%20it%20back%20home%20%E2%80%93%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20grandeur%20of%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20soaring%20peaks%2C%20challenging%20climate%2C%20unparalleled%20scenic%20beauty%20and%20just%20the%20correct%20amount%20of%20sweetness%20of%20its%20gentle%20friendly%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Ajoy%20Ashirwad%20Mahaprashasta%3A%20Ragi%20mudde%20and%20nati%20koli%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20mudde%3C%2Fem%3E%20(ragi%20balls)%20and%20%3Cem%3Enati%20koli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(country%20chicken)%20curry%20I%20ate%20during%20my%20election%20tour%20in%20Karnataka%20was%20a%20meal%20to%20remember.%20Making%20the%20mudde%20is%20an%20extremely%20painstaking%20process.%20Traditionally%2C%20ragi%2C%20or%20whole%20grain%20finger%20millet%2C%20is%20first%20milled%20to%20flour%2C%20slowly%20cooked%20into%20a%20dough%2C%20and%20rolled%20for%20at%20least%20an%20hour%20to%20be%20eaten%20as%20soft%20and%20moist%20balls.%20It%20may%20be%20an%20acquired%20taste%20for%20many%2C%20but%20its%20combination%20with%20the%20delicious%20village-style%20chicken%20curry%20fills%20you%20with%20energy%20that%20easily%20lasts%20for%20a%20day.%20Hugely%20popular%20in%20Old%20Mysore%2C%20the%20mudde%20characterises%20all%20the%20strength%2C%20grit%20and%20love%20that%20transformed%20the%20region%20into%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prosperous%20regions%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Sangeeta%20Barooah%20Pisharoty%3A%20Khaar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20dish%20that%20forms%20part%20of%20a%20homemade%20Sunday%20meal.%20We%20call%20it%20%3Cem%3Ekhaar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20marker%20of%20my%20identity%20as%20an%20Assamese.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhaar%20is%20a%20black%20alkaline%20liquid%20methodically%20extracted%20from%20the%20peel%20%E2%80%93%20burnt%20or%20sun-dried%20%E2%80%93%20of%20a%20ripe%20banana%20of%20a%20local%20variety%20found%20in%20Northeast%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhaar%20can%20be%20both%20vegetarian%20and%20otherwise.%20Two%20of%20the%20varieties%20I%20savour%20the%20most%20are%20made%20with%20dried%20jasmine%20flowers%20and%20with%20cucumber%20and%20black%20chickpeas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETry%20any%20of%20the%20khaar%20preparations%20(including%20a%20yummy%20one%20made%20with%20pork)%20not%20just%20to%20have%20a%20finger-licking%20experience%20but%20also%20to%20understand%20why%20I%20frequently%20call%20it%20the%20fifth%20flavour%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20equivalent%20to%20the%20Japanese%20umami!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Seema%20Chishti%3A%20Bread%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20ended%20with%20reading%20about%20and%20staring%20at%20Gaza%20bakeries%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20war%20by%20Israel.%20Just%20seeing%20and%20reading%20about%20the%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Ebread%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0that%20kept%20the%20population%20of%202.2%20million%20alive%20till%20it%20did%2C%C2%A0the%20long%20queues%20for%20it%20made%20an%20impact.%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EBread%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20freshly%20baked%20or%20not%2C%20seemed%20to%20mean%20so%20much%20more%2C%20as%20this%20year%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Soumashree%20Sarkar%3A%20Tea%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20year%20when%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20in%20Kolkata%20ends%2C%20giant%20idols%20from%20around%20the%20city%20make%20their%20way%20to%20the%20banks%20by%20the%20Ganga%20for%20a%20bittersweet%20immersion.%20The%20result%20is%20chaos%20beyond%20your%20wildest%20dreams%20%E2%80%93%20exactly%20the%20thing%20that%20draws%20people%20to%20witness%20the%20end%20of%20the%20festivities.%20This%20year%2C%20it%20rained%20on%20Dashami%2C%20the%20day%20the%20immersion%20process%20starts.%20One%20second%2C%20the%20river%20was%20red%20with%20the%20setting%20sun%2C%20and%20the%20next%2C%20it%20was%20at%20one%20with%20the%20sky%20in%20a%20singular%20wash.%20After%20the%20rains%20ended%2C%20I%20drank%20some%20milky%2C%20sweet%20tea%20while%20more%20idols%20were%20sent%20homewards%20into%20the%20river.%20It%20made%20me%20think%20that%20in%20every%20ending%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sweet%20beginning%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Taniya%20Roy%3A%20Croissant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20croissant%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%2030%20years.%20I%20binged%20on%20it%20day%20and%20night%20during%20my%20trip%20to%20Barcelona.%20You%20know%20that%20feeling%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20so%20happy%20that%20you%20cannot%20stop%20eating%20your%20favourite%20food%3F%20Well%2C%20the%20croissant%20became%20my%20absolute%20favourite%20during%20my%20time%20in%20Spain.%20Although%20I%20tried%20other%20items%2C%20nothing%20could%20compete%20with%20a%20freshly%20baked%20butter%20croissant.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20need%20anything%20else%20with%20it%20%E2%80%93%20just%20the%20croissant.%20I%20was%20totally%20obsessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E9.%20Aathira%20Perinchery%3A%20Paal%20kappa%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99m%20Keralite%20alright%2C%20but%20I%20had%20paal%20kappa%20for%20the%20first%20time%20only%20some%20time%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Fluffy%20and%20filling%2C%20creamy%20but%20comforting%2C%20this%20dish%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20mashed%20tapioca%20and%20coconut%20milk.%20Pair%20it%20with%20a%20mean%20meen%20curry%20or%20some%20succulent%20beef%20roast!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E10.%20Jahnavi%20Sen%3A%20Laphing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20Humayunpur%20in%20Delhi%2C%20a%20friend%20suggested%20I%20try%20the%20laphing%20from%20a%20stall%20on%20the%20road%20%E2%80%93%20and%20now%20I%20crave%20it%20frequently.%20This%20Tibetan%20dish%20is%20a%20cold%20noodle%20wrapped%20around%20dried%20red%20chillies%2C%20a%20garlic%20paste%20and%20minced%20meat%2Fchicken%20or%20vegetables%2C%20and%20the%20version%20I%20had%20also%20had%20some%20wai-wai%20in%20it%20for%20crunch.%20Even%20the%20%E2%80%98medium%20spicy%E2%80%99%20very%20was%20quite%20fiery%2C%20and%20mouth-%20(and%20eye-)wateringly%20delicious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E11.%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%3A%20Kolhapuri%20mutton%20in%20Pune%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20lecture%20I%20gave%20in%20Pune%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20organisers%20took%20me%20to%20%E2%80%98Dehaati%E2%80%99%20on%20Prabhat%20Road%2C%20famous%20for%20its%20Kolhapuri%20thalis.%20I%20had%20a%20mutton%20pickle%20dish%2C%20%3Cem%3Eloonche%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20with%20jowar%20rotis%20and%20endless%20amounts%20of%20tamda%20rassa%20and%20pandhra%20rasa%2C%20two%20delicious%20mutton%20gravies%20%E2%80%93%20one%20red%2C%20the%20other%20white%20%E2%80%93%20that%20Kolhapur%20is%20famous%20for.%20The%20meal%20was%20made%20all%20the%20more%20enjoyable%20by%20the%20background%20music%20the%20restaurant%20was%20playing%3A%20Siddheshwari%20Devi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703813407000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F28182156%2Ffood.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Fthe-wire-recommends-the-meals-we-remember-from-2023%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Fthe-wire-recommends-the-meals-we-remember-fr