%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20others%20like%2050%20Cent%20and%20Ja-Rule%20who%20were%20beefing%20at%20the%20time%20and%20putting%20out%20music%2C%20but%20the%20first%20Hip%20Hop%20artist%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20was%20Eminem.%20His%20fearless%20storytelling%2C%20humour%20and%20the%20music%20itself%20made%20me%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20this%20genre.%20The%20whole%20scene%20was%20hot%20and%20I%20think%20I%20discovered%20Hip%20Hop%20at%20the%20right%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20Moko%20recalls%20how%20he%20was%20a%20timid%20and%20shy%20person%20who%20was%20scared%20to%20talk%20in%20front%20of%20people.%20Hip%20Hop%20helped%20him%20find%20his%20voice.%20%E2%80%9CHip%20Hop%20was%20like%20a%20second%20father%20to%20me.%20It%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20to%20express%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoko%20was%2014%20when%20he%20wrote%20his%20first%20song%20and%20two%20years%20later%20composed%20and%20recorded%20his%20first%20song%20%E2%80%98Listen%20to%20Your%20Heart%E2%80%99%20on%20a%20mobile%20phone%20at%20his%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20place.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20song%20I%20recorded%20was%20on%20a%20phone.%20I%20transferred%20the%20audio%20to%20a%20computer%20and%20used%20a%20software%20called%20Virtual%20DJ%20where%20I%20had%20to%20sync%20the%20music%20and%20audio%20without%20any%20mixing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reminisces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20writing%20songs%20and%20making%20music%2C%20Moko%20was%20also%20a%20good%20student.%20After%20high%20school%2C%20he%20got%20into%20the%20prestigious%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259970%2Fmiracradle-niranjan-thomas-india-asphyxia-newborns-treatment-low-cost-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristian%20Medical%20College%20(CMC)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Vellore%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20to%20study%20medicine%20but%20turned%20down%20the%20opportunity%20to%20study%20there.%20He%20makes%20a%20reference%20to%20this%20event%20in%20the%20first%20verse%20of%20his%20latest%20single%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAji%20Kali%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20released%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FbylHAbo9yw8%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FbylHAbo9yw8%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20did%20he%20decide%20not%20to%20pursue%20medicine%20from%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20medical%20colleges%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20leave%20Kohima.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20he%20argues%20that%20pursuing%20his%20graduation%20at%20the%20Kohima%20Science%20College%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cplus%20point%E2%80%9D%20in%20helping%20him%20mould%20his%20craft%20as%20a%20rapper%20and%20performer.%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20demands%20of%20medical%20school%2C%20maybe%20if%20I%20had%20gone%20out%20to%20study%20there%2C%20I%20would%20be%20a%20doctor%20now%20instead%20of%20a%20rapper%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20college%20functions%2C%20I%20would%20always%20take%20the%20opportunity%20to%20get%20on%20stage%20and%20perform%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20away%20with%20stage%20fright.%20In%20the%20years%20I%20spent%20in%20college%2C%20I%20would%20always%20request%20my%20seniors%20to%20let%20me%20perform%20on%20stage%20and%20they%20would%20give%20me%20a%20chance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20as%20he%20was%20coming%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20Anthropology%2C%20he%20began%20performing%20in%20front%20of%20live%20audiences%20and%20earning%20some%20money%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20has%20always%20been%20supportive%20of%20my%20music.%20During%20my%20college%20days%2C%20I%20never%20flunked%20out%2C%20brought%20bad%20grades%20or%20got%20held%20up%20by%20%E2%80%98back%20papers%E2%80%99.%20That%20allowed%20my%20family%20to%20trust%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20with%20my%20life.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20was%20making%20music%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20college%2C%20making%20music%20started%20as%20a%20hobby%20but%20soon%20turned%20into%20a%20passion.%20In%202017%2C%20I%20performed%20in%20front%20of%20a%20live%20audience%20and%20got%20paid%20for%20the%20very%20first%20time.%20This%20is%20how%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20can%20pursue%20music%20as%20a%20professional%20career%20instead%20of%20studying%2C%20giving%20exams%2C%20and%20pursuing%20government%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20any%20artist%20starting%20out%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20pay%20for%20studio%20sessions%20when%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it.%20Early%20on%2C%20Moko%20would%20borrow%20money%20from%20his%20mother%20to%20pay%20for%20these%20sessions%20because%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20proper%20recording%20studio%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsg1wDKPawL%2F%3Futm_sour